sub_title: Diagnostics Intern at ITER Organization. Candidate for M.Sc. in Science and Technology of Nuclear Fusion at Eindhoven University of Technology
summary:
Nuclear fusion master’s student committed to applying physics and engineering skills toward clean energy
technology and climate change mitigation. Experienced in the energy industry and research, with a particular
affinity for hands-on work and creative problem-solving. Searching for full-time opportunities following my graduation in summer 2023.
